<commentary>nīpam iti || sāraṅgā mataṅgajāḥ kuraṅgā bhṛṅgā vā || "sāraṅgaś cātake bhṛṅge kuraṅge ca mataṅgaje" iti viśvaḥ || ardharūḍhair ekadeśodgataiḥ kesaraiḥ kiñjalkair haritaṃ pālāśavarṇa kapiśaṃ kṛṣṇapītaṃ ca || "pālāśo harito harit" iti | "śyāvaḥ syāt kapiśo dhūmradhūmalau kṛṣṇalohite" iti cāmaraḥ || śyāmavarṇam iti yāvat || "varṇo varṇena" iti samāsaḥ || nīpaṃ sthalakadambakusumam || "atha sthakadambake | nīpaḥ syāt pulake" iti śabdārṇave || dṛṣṭvā saṃprekṣya | viditveti yāvat | tathā kacchev anukaccham ||  || "avyayaṃ vibhakti-" ityādinā vibhaktyarthe 'vyayībhāvaḥ || "jalapāyam anūpaṃ syāt puṃsi kacchas tathāvidhaḥ" ity amaraḥ || āvirbhūtāḥ prathamāḥ prathamotpannā mukulā yāsāṃ tāḥ kandalīr bhūmikadalīḥ || "droṇaparṇī snigdhakandā kandalī bhūkadaly api iti śabdārṇave || jagdhvā bhakṣayitvā || "ado jagdhiḥ-" iti jagdhyādeśaḥ || araṇyeṣv adhikasurabhim atighrāṇatarpaṇaṃ "dagdhāraṇyeṣu" iti pāṭhe "dagdham" ity adhikaviśeṣaṇam || arthavaśāt kandalīś ca dṛṣṭvaivety anvayo draṣṭavyaḥ || urvyā bhūmer gandham āghrāya jalalavamuco meghasya te tava mārgaṃ sūcayiṣyanty anumāpayiṣyanti | yatra yatra vṛṣṭikāryaṃ kandalīmukulanīpakusumādikaṃ dṛśyate tatra tatraḥ tvayā vṛṣṭam ity anumīyata iti bhāvaḥ ||</commentary>